2 (4) The department shall use the money deposited in the account in the state special revenue fund
3 as provided in subsection (3) to provide grants, using criteria established by the department, to Montana-based
4 nonprofit organizations that promote awareness and enhance education regarding motorcycle safety.
5 (5) The account in the state special revenue fund provided for in subsection (3) is statutorily
6 appropriated to the department, as provided in 17-7-502.
